title: Exodus wallet coin Latest Release 1.58.2
description:
Ripple has never looked this good, transactions in Exodus have never been this fast. Seamlessly send, receive, and exchange at the touch of a button and give your Ripple the beautiful home it deserves! 

For all you veteran traders, we’ve also added our first fully-supported, dollar-backed stablecoin to the wallet and exchange, TrueUSD. In addition, Mac customers will now be able to upgrade automatically to future versions of Exodus when logging into their wallets. Wow! That’s a lot of content crammed into one release, maybe we should let our developers sleep... 

Settings 
Changing fiat currencies no longer causes the app to crash. 
Advanced 
The developer menu reduces confusion by having one option to move funds from a Ripple private key or secret key
